<plot>Is a light amusing story about Nesio, a small time drug dealer who has never managed to get away from his mother or his childhood traumas, and carries on his back the stigma of a boom loser. This he struggles to overcome, but finds it impossible. By intent or otherwise, Nesio becomes involved in a homicide and impossible love with a masked women. All of this framed by downtown Mexico City.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?393295</url></doc>
